Adobe InCopy CC 2019 ACC

Adobe InCopy CC 2019 – a program for the professional creation and editing of materials, closely associated with the program Adobe InDesign CC 2018 to improve the interaction of design teams and editors. Adobe InCopy CC 2019 is ideal for large projects where many people work on text and graphic design.

Adobe InCopy CC 2019 is part of Creative Cloud . Therefore, all the latest updates are available to its users, and access to new versions is available from the moment of their release. Improve your skills and master new tools with a large and constantly updated collection of training videos. Thanks to the integration with Behance, you can share your projects with other users and instantly receive feedback on your work from designers from around the world.
Advantages of Adobe InCopy CC 2019: 

– Footnotes for multiple columns
– OpenType improvements
– Updated interface
– Simplified work with glyphs
– Placement in image tables
– Simple addition of shading to the text; includes offset management tools and much more
